            "pathId": 2653838727973464043,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女はゴールドシチーの走る姿が『キレイ』\nだったと告げた。だが、ゴールドシチーは\n『強い』と言われてみたかったと零す。",
            "enText": "She told her that Gold City looked \n\"beautiful\" when she ran. But Gold City said \nshe wanted to be called \"strong.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 178,
                    "pathId": 4390191983400654273
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 187,
                    "pathId": -3260826293524994635
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 259,
                    "pathId": -8909634562386480217
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": -4635790440208979440
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6886355725503242741,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "すると、ユキノビジンは『キレイ』は\r\n見た目だけの言葉じゃないと主張する。\n強いも、すごいも、全部が含まれた言葉だと。",
            "enText": "Yukinobijin then insists that \"beautiful\" is \nnot just a word for appearance. It is a word \nthat includes everything, including strong \nand amazing.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 121,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 2918742044620198294
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 203,
                    "pathId": -5319494537024900451
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 259,
                    "pathId": -1559317418052976660
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 215,
                    "pathId": 2713235942973202438
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2256639218006010646,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――思い返すと、確かに走りも含め全部を\n評価してくれていた人もいたのかもしれない。\n気づくと同時に、ゴールドシチーは笑った。",
            "enText": "―Looking back, I realize that there may have \nbeen people who appreciated everything about \nthe race, including the way I ran. As soon \nas she realized, Gold City laughed.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 174,
                    "pathId": -5566908746677790326
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 177,
                    "pathId": 8603641059843121548
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 259,
                    "pathId": 4948407883647938465
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 183,
                    "pathId": -1458368205161437203
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6133764180610094340,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "心から笑うゴールドシチーは本当にキレイで\n1番好きだと、ユキノビジンが言う。\nゴールドシチーも、同じだと頷くのだった。",
            "enText": "Yukino Bijin says that Gold City, with \nits hearty laugh, is really beautiful \nand her favorite. Gold City nodded \nher head in agreement.",
